# Rust GDExtension (rust_ext/) - built DLLs are large, platform-specific,
# and regenerable via `cargo build [--release]` in rust_ext/. See
# rust_ext/README.md for build/troubleshooting notes. Anyone pulling this
# repo needs to build once locally before the extension loads - the
# .gdextension file's paths point at these now-ignored locations on purpose.
# Cargo.lock IS committed (cdylib/application target, not a library - locking
# exact dependency versions matters more than it would for a published crate).
rust_ext/target/
